snippet: The Moiseyev Dance Company and three other troupes offered high-energy performances at the Fall for Dance festival at City Center.
abstract: Alastair Macaulay reviews Fall for Dance festival program, featuring performances by dance companies Moiseyev Dance Company, Ballet West, Tu Dance and Nan Jombang, at City Center.
lead_paragraph: The Moiseyev Dance Company and three other troupes offered high-energy performances at the Fall for Dance festival at City Center.
